{"tid":755581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喜劇片《阿勇的自白》下架       或將推出重拍版本","createTime":"2018-07-25T10:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T11:35:18.000Z","uid":15696,"like":103,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a316008d5e0c425424be4aef1d87e664f8e7644d","tid":755581,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"由新晉導演潘九杰及霍秋泳執導，獨立製作的喜劇片《阿勇的自白》今日一上架，已經成為網民熱話。其中主演這場「獨腳戲」的譚智東，更演活了「阿勇」這個患有智能障礙的宅男，不但被人騙盡金錢愛情，更要拍片為騙子辯護，成功得到不少人恥笑及同情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於大受歡迎，片段疑似已被電影公司購買，已經在平台刪除。潘九杰表示短片即將被重拍，在製作方面將更認真，不會再在霍秋泳的黃大仙寓所樓下拍攝，道具方面，亦會用A4紙取代表霍秋泳母校的單行紙。講到網民對片段穿崩位十分眼利，九杰不禁吠叫了幾聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網民將《阿勇的自白》備份：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrEkLHVtynio&d=ldkSIQ05jxfPpNtjU%2FieM%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=73a0a051\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民對片段穿崩位十分眼利：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/145119_5fe81018756b127cf6c03f2c9a93bb5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F145119_5fe81018756b127cf6c03f2c9a93bb5e.png&h=f69e9050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/153958_b7077b1be0289f3a15dd2d3bde15d0a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F153958_b7077b1be0289f3a15dd2d3bde15d0a3.png&h=08c230d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7caad3f90e0d72cdc23dd9f0d8c01f48042cd2","tid":755581,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g